s. We can assure our oncology patients and their families that they will continue to receive outstanding and effective care at DHMC.\"','2012-02-16T15:24:50+0000',0,207660,'2014-10-29 12:06:54'),('10150117443575462_10151279268165462','b5d78332adadf26df7823f736f21627664b878b0','The last thing you_d expect as a 35-year-old personal trainer and fitness instructor_ who doesn_t drink or smoke_ is to be diagnosed with cancer. http://cancer.dartmouth.edu/pf/ps_jennifer.html','2012-02-15T22:19:39+0000','10151279268105462_14041065','a816a71f11f51088bd9891feb471098df2ade84f',0,'I was fortunate enough to have Dr. Paydafar, who is without hesitation the most exceptional surgeon I have met. He took the time to explain everything to my husband, who needed more support than I did. He sensed that and dealt with it patiently and compassionately.','2012-02-15T22:35:20+0000',1,207661,'2014-10-29 12:06:54'),('10150117443575462_10151279268165462','b5d78332adadf26df7823f736f21627664b878b0','The last thing you_d expect as a 35-year-old personal trainer and fitness instructor_ who doesn_t drink or smoke_ is to be diagnosed with cancer. http://cancer.dartmouth.edu/pf/ps_jennifer.html','2012-02-15T22:19:39+0000','10151279268105462_14046478','b5d78332adadf26df7823f736f21627664b878b0',0,'Thank you so much, Dawn! We\'ll send your kind words on to Dr. Paydarfar.','2012-02-16T13:44:21+0000',0,207662,'2014-10-29 12:06:54'),('10150117443575462_10151276960590462','b5d78332adadf26df7823f736f21627664b878b0',NULL,'2012-02-15T10:23:56+0000','10151276858250462_29932039','b5d78332adadf26df7823f736f21627664b878b0',0,'Photos from Patient and Family Support Service\'s Valentine\'s Day Comfort Cart tour of the Cancer Center. A sweet and delicious day!','2012-02-15T10:25:24+0000',0,207663,'2014-10-29 12:06:54'),('10150117443575462_10151276960590462','b5d78332adadf26df7823f736f21627664b878b0',NULL,'2012-02-15T10:23:56+0000','10151276858250462_29960517','b5d78332adadf26df7823f736f21627664b878b0',0,'These fine ph