th-hitchcock.org/health_information/flu_vaccine_information.html.    -Victoria','2013-10-03T14:05:55+0000','10153268442550462_21144399','63f3d730fa422ee6d4f857e4dba87d10ef6e2518',0,'Thank you for sharing your story Victoria Brady McCandless.','2013-10-03T14:50:45+0000',2,207728,'2014-10-29 12:07:26'),('10150117443575462_10153265216275462','b5d78332adadf26df7823f736f21627664b878b0','Superheros to the rescue. Window washers bring joy to our littlest patients.  ','2013-10-02T16:05:28+0000','10153265216275462_43218404','b5d78332adadf26df7823f736f21627664b878b0',0,'A crowd gathers to watch.','2013-10-02T16:11:17+0000',0,207729,'2014-10-29 12:07:26'),('10150117443575462_10153238876700462','b5d78332adadf26df7823f736f21627664b878b0','Check out our healthy harvest from the Healing Garden outside the Infusion Suite in Nashua. Chemo patients have watched the growth all summer and now they can take fresh veggies home to enjoy.  Amy Welch_ RN_ sets out a stack of just picked treats for patients to choose from.','2013-09-24T16:12:23+0000','10153238876595462_21045033','b4b500dea5f97ab6de25a044e7dc8b36e3755a03',0,'AWSOME!! Hi Amy, I Miss Youu...You Look Fabulous!!!','2013-09-24T18:36:56+0000',2,207730,'2014-10-29 12:07:26'),('10150117443575462_10153238876700462','b5d78332adadf26df7823f736f21627664b878b0','Check out our healthy harvest from the Healing Garden outside the Infusion Suite in Nashua. Chemo patients have watched the growth all summer and now they can take fresh veggies home to enjoy.  Amy Welch_ RN_ sets out a stack of just picked treats for patients to choose from.','2013-09-24T16:12:23+0000','10153238876595462_21049241','a48ed462407b47c32d1c74d1d141015aad51e46e',0,'Thanks Dee! Miss you too!','2013-09-25T01:43:37+0000',1,207731,'2014-10-29 12:07:26'),('10150117443575462_10153238876700462','b5d78332adadf26df7823f736f21627664b878b0','Check out our healthy harvest from the Healing Garden outside the Infusion Suite in Nashua. Chemo patients have watched the growth all summe