7443575462_10152790235875462','1e5ed02933c5d56bfbbfc1b4e3034893df1223c5','I am a citizen of South Africa. I read the article on THS (third hand smoking). I smoke in my own home and car only. Does this actually mean that I shall NEVER be able to hold my 5 month old baby girl in my arms OR even visit her at her parents house? Devistated. HW du Plessis.','2013-05-15T20:07:08+0000','10152790235875462_40123873','b5d78332adadf26df7823f736f21627664b878b0',0,'At the moment, we still do not know how much of a risk third hand smoke carries, but the safest option is to stop smoking completely. There are many methods that have been proven to be helpful in treating tobacco dependence, and I would suggest that you speak with your doctor to help you quit. If this is not possible, I suggest that you wash your hands well after using tobacco, and try to wear clothes while cuddling with your baby that have not been worn while you were smoking. It would also be safest for your baby\'s health for you to only smoke OUTSIDE, and not while your daughter is present. Smoking inside the home or inside the car makes for a space that has a lot of toxins that your baby can breathe in, absorb through her skin, or eat from dust (once she starts crawling). I wish you good health, and I am hopeful you can quit smoking to best protect your baby.','2013-05-15T20:55:12+0000',1,207795,'2014-10-29 12:07:26'),('10150117443575462_10152772363190462','b5d78332adadf26df7823f736f21627664b878b0','What moms inspire you? This young mother inspired us. She survived breast cancer and wrote a book to help children understand the illness. Proceeds support cancer research. And the little girl illustrated on each page_ the author_s dauther_ will graduate this spring. And mom will be there to see it.','2013-05-12T12:00:00+0000','10152772363190462_40041921','a3e2a91c44e58a0c28ce0130818646bd6a4b4c16',0,'What a great idea, very sweet illustrations. Two time cancer survivorâ€”Wow.','2013-05-12T12:38:19+0000',0,207796,'2014-