INSERT INTO `_1_post` VALUES ('photo','post_page_378004348924081','Oats with Bananas and Raisins    Ingredients:  2 cups rolled oats  1 Â½ cups apple juice or orange juice  1 cup yoghurt  Â½ cup milk  2 tablespoons honey  Â½ banana_ sliced  raisins    Method:  used 3 oranges to get 1 Â½ cups of orange juice.  Place rolled oats in a big bowl.  Pour orange juice over the rolled oats and mixed well. Cover and refrigerate at least 2 hours_ best is overnight.  Add yoghurt_ milk and honey to the rolled oats mixture. Stir until all combined.  Serve with banana and raisins on top    t doesnâ€™t look appetising but it is very nice and healthy. Best of all no cooking involve (:','https://fbcdn-sphotos-d-a.akamaihd.net/hphotos-ak-xpa1/v/t1.0-9/s130x130/71660_459177514140097_1301687663_n.jpg?oh=45a9873397cfcb14a16f3c485d9f82e6&oe=54BA8A16&__gda__=1424875371_e35a79a1fbde73ee748c2c46d5d4cfcc','https://www.facebook.com/365cps/photos/a.380809678643548.87582.378004348924081/459177514140097/?type=1&relevant_count=1','facebook.com','2012-12-31T03:59:16+0000',1356926356,1,1,0,0,0,0,0,1,'378004348924081_459177540806761','https://www.facebook.com/378004348924081/posts/459177540806761','365 Cancer Prevention Society',411,'2014-10-29 05:01:35',1),('photo','post_page_378004348924081','Apple Avocado Salad with Tangerine Dressing    Ingredients :     1 (10 ounce) package baby greens   1/4 cup chopped red onion   1/2 cup chopped walnuts   1/3 cup crumbled blue cheese   2 teaspoons lemon zest   1 apple - peeled_ cored and sliced   1 avocado - peeled_ pitted and diced   4 mandarin oranges_ juiced   1/2 lemon_ juiced   1/2 teaspoon lemon zest   1 clove garlic_ minced   2 tablespoons olive oil   salt to taste    Directions:  In a large bowl_ toss together the baby greens_ red onion_ walnuts_ blue cheese_ and lemon zest. Mix in the apple and avocado just before serving.  In a container with a lid_ mix the mandarin orange juice_ lemon juice_ lemon zest_ garlic_ olive oil_ and salt. Drizzle over the salad as desired.','https://fbcdn-sphotos-c-a.akamaihd.net/hphotos-ak-xaf1/v/t1.0-9/p128x128/548077_459175660806949_169892882_n.jpg?oh=d35cd202aa7be3bc02db81dbe49d5348&oe=54F161E1&__gda__=1425011902_fa92dabf62167bc7c744c90670ec1a8c','https://www.facebook.com/365cps/photos/a.380809678643548.87582.378004348924081/459175660806949/?type=1&relevant_count=1','facebook.com','2012-12-31T03:52:56+0000',1356925976,6,7,0,0,0,0,0,6,'378004348924081_459175680806947','https://www.facebook.com/378004348924081/posts/459175680806947','365 Cancer Prevention Society',412,'2014-10-29 05:01:35',1),('status','post_page_378004348924081','Q: What is a _good diet_ for someone currently undergoing both chemo and radiotherapy for cancer treatment?  A: A â€˜goodâ€™ diet would be one that is balanced i.e. contains a good mix and vegetables and meat_ avoiding extremely sweet_ salty and oily foods. Preferred cooking methods would be steaming _boiling and stir frying rather than deep frying_ grilling_ baking.  Subjecting animal protein to high heat during deep frying_ grilling_ barbequeing_ baking_ will create heterocyclic amines which is carcinogenic. Minimize eating this foods but allow patient to try a little to ensure enough food intake as his/her taste and smell functions are altered_ leading to reduced appetite. Do not be too stringent on food choice during cancer therapies.',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2012-12-31T03:45:05+0000',1356925505,2,2,0,0,0,0,0,2,'378004348924081_459173937473788','https://www.facebook.com/378004348924081/posts/459173937473788','365 Cancer Prevention Society',413,'2014-10-29 05:01:35',1),('photo','post_page_378004348924081','This low fat recipe really is a healthy food_ and the banana bread is great for snacks_ lunch boxes or desserts. It_s also a brilliant way to use up bananas which are verging on becoming over-ripe and too squidgy to eat - these ones have an especially intense flavour and mash down easily to add to your cake batter.     I used four very ripe bananas to make this recipe and the fruity aroma came wafting from the oven as it cooked. It almost tastes like a vanilla cake_ because it_s so full of fragrance and flavour.    This banana bread doesn_t contain any fatapart from what occurs naturally in the walnuts_ it_s all been replaced with apple puree (applesauce). To make apple puree_ peel_ core and slice cooking apples such as Bramleys. You need 3-4 to make 2 cups of applesauce. Place in a pan with some water and cook gently until the apples are soft enough to mash to a pulp. Store for up to a week in the fridge_ or freeze in an ice tray to use as needed for baking.','https://fbcdn-sphotos-d-a.akamaihd.net/hphotos-ak-xfa1/v/t1.0-9/s130x130/313986_457917424266106_2117896707_n.jpg?oh=36474827ae2b6b85f8c00bc7b761063b&oe=54B7315D&__gda__=1424932072_3b29930ed0b7effc07e5048dfd499ea9','https://www.facebook.com/365cps/photos/a.380809678643548.87582.378004348924081/457917424266106/?type=1&relevant_count=1','facebook.com','2012-12-28T06:41:17+0000',1356676877,2,2,0,0,0,0,0,2,'378004348924081_457917434266105','https://www.facebook.com/378004348924081/posts/457917434266105','365 Cancer Prevention Society',414,'2014-10-29 05:01:35',1),('photo','post_page_378004348924081','Laugh as much as you breathe and love as long as you live.','https://fbcdn-sphotos-c-a.akamaihd.net/hphotos-ak-xpa1/v/t1.0-9/s130x130/15422_457916140932901_1264898938_n.jpg?oh=261db3f603de0ba26d43cf09dd1c53cc&oe=54B435CC&__gda__=1425554609_a9e66c5b023c9c1254cefa0442fdb88b','https://www.facebook.com/365cps/photos/a.380809678643548.87582.378004348924081/457916140932901/?type=1&relevant_count=1','facebook.com','2012-12-28T06:34:58+0000',1356676498,1,1,0,0,0,0,0,1,'378004348924081_457916157599566','https://www.facebook.com/378004348924081/posts/457916157599566','365 Cancer Prevention Society',415,'2014-10-29 05:01:35',1),('status','post_page_378004348924081','_I will be a role model for cancer patients for the rest of my life. But you know what? When I was getting chemo_ those people inspired me_  - Eric Davis',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2012-12-28T06:32:38+0000',1356676358,4,4,0,0,0,0,0,4,'378004348924081_457915437599638','https://www.facebook.com/378004348924081/posts/457915437599638','365 Cancer Prevention Society',416,'2014-10-29 05:01:35',1),('status','post_page_378004348924081','There is something good in all seeming failures. You are not to see that now. Time will reveal it. Be patient!',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2012-12-28T06:31:42+0000',1356676302,2,2,0,0,0,0,0,2,'378004348924081_457915287599653','https://www.facebook.com/378004348924081/posts/457915287599653','365 Cancer Prevention Society',417,'2014-10-29 05:01:35',1),('photo','post_page_378004348924081','CCIS = CELEBRATING CHRISTMAS IN SINGAPORE! <3','https://fbcdn-sphotos-c-a.akamaihd.net/hphotos-ak-xfp1/v/t1.0-9/s130x130/734120_457912787599903_445255119_n.jpg?oh=09b1ee19dfebdb8f02dfccd3a671f13f&oe=54BDDBB3&__gda__=1421612208_2b180cb00fe9a3c267c0a6a4091fd6a8','https://www.facebook.com/365cps/photos/a.457912727599909.106764.378004348924081/457912787599903/?type=1&relevant_count=31','facebook.com','2012-12-28T06:29:44+0000',1356676184,3,3,0,0,0,0,0,3,'378004348924081_457914844266364','https://www.facebook.com/378004348924081/posts/457914844266364','365 Cancer Prevention Society',418,'2014-10-29 05:01:35',1),('photo','post_page_378004348924081','Come spot us at our booth outside wisma!','https://scontent-a.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-xaf1/v/t1.0-9/s130x130/312572_453943504663498_518057942_n.jpg?oh=f7ed4a548d156defcd1746c382711712&oe=54ECB80A','https://www.facebook.com/365cps/photos/a.380809678643548.87582.378004348924081/453943504663498/?type=1&relevant_count=1','facebook.com','2012-12-19T10:56:32+0000',1355914592,9,9,0,0,0,0,0,9,'378004348924081_453943517996830','https://www.facebook.com/378004348924081/posts/453943517996830','365 Cancer Prevention Society',419,'2014-10-29 05:01:35',1),('photo','post_page_378004348924081','Fantastic batch of balloon sculpture volunteers from everywhere! All getting ready for next week_s LOVESTICKS! fundraising event. COME & find us @ orchard (outside Wisma) & buy a Christmas balloon home! :D','https://scontent-a.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-xpa1/v/t1.0-9/s130x130/68989_451297204928128_337877128_n.jpg?oh=6e64bbf61bcd369a684d1db310213422&oe=54BB73D0','https://www.facebook.com/365cps/photos/a.380809678643548.87582.378004348924081/451297204928128/?type=1&relevant_count=1','facebook.com','2012-12-13T14:01:14+0000',1355407274,12,12,0,0,0,0,0,12,'378004348924081_451297224928126','https://www.facebook.com/378004348924081/posts/451297224928126','365 Cancer Prevention Society',420,'2014-10-29 05:01:35',1),('photo','post_page_378004348924081','Our CHRISTMAS _LOVE LUNCH_ party with the Cancer Patients and Volunteers.','https://fbcdn-sphotos-f-a.akamaihd.net/hphotos-ak-xfa1/v/t1.0-9/s130x130/27901_451158471608668_1343055004_n.jpg?oh=37d69fbb18972ae498eb3cfcf495d02a&oe=54BD66A1&__gda__=1420807174_90ea2c4b33d66999a487882584da7d70','https://www.facebook.com/365cps/photos/a.380809678643548.87582.378004348924081/451158471608668/?type=1&relevant_count=1','facebook.com','2012-12-13T04:38:49+0000',1355373529,6,7,1,1,0,0,0,7,'378004348924081_451158501608665','https://www.facebook.com/378004348924081/posts/451158501608665','365 Cancer Prevention Society',421,'2014-10-29 05:01:35',1),('photo','post_page_378004348924081','Feed your faith and your fears will starve to death!','https://scontent-a.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-xaf1/v/t1.0-9/s130x130/548600_450748174983031_1716222136_n.jpg?oh=cac9bb8e67de23b3cc9d4112683a0b0c&oe=54EE0643','https://www.facebook.com/365cps/photos/a.380809678643548.87582.378004348924081/450748174983031/?type=1&relevant_count=1','facebook.com','2012-12-12T07:26:22+0000',1355297182,2,2,0,0,0,0,0,2,'378004348924081_450748184983030','https://www.facebook.com/378004348924081/posts/450748184983030','365 Cancer Prevention Society',422,'2014-10-29 05:01:35',1),('photo','post_page_378004348924081','Ginger Angel Food Cake    Ingredients  For the cake:  1 cup minus 1 tablespoon cake flour  1 1/2 cups confectioners_ sugar_ plus more for topping  1/4 teaspoon salt  11 large egg whites_ at room temperature  1 1/2 teaspoons cream of tartar  1 cup granulated sugar  1 teaspoon vanilla extract  1 teaspoon finely grated lime zest  3 tablespoons finely grated peeled ginger  For the sauce:  3 half pints raspberries  1/3 cup granulated sugar  1/2 teaspoon finely grated lime zest  1 teaspoon fresh lime juice  Directions  Make the cake: Preheat the oven to 350 degrees F. Sift the flour_ confectioners_ sugar and salt onto a sheet of parchment paper. Sift again_ then set aside.    Beat the egg whites in a large bowl with a mixer on medium speed until frothy. Add the cream of tartar and beat until soft peaks form_ about 5 minutes. Gradually beat in the granulated sugar_ about 1 tablespoon at a time_ then increase the speed to medium high and continue beating until stiff_ shiny peaks form_ 12 to 15 minutes. Add the vanilla_ lime zest and ginger and beat a few seconds to combine.    Sprinkle one-quarter of the flour mixture over the egg mixture and gently fold with a rubber spatula. Fold in the remaining flour mixture in 3 additions. Transfer the batter to an ungreased 10-inch tube pan. Bake until the cake feels springy and a toothpick inserted into the center comes out clean_ 40 to 50 minutes. Invert the pan onto a funnel or the neck of a bottle and cool completely. Loosen the edges with a small knife_ tap the sides of the pan against the counter and unmold.    Make the sauce: Puree 2 half pints raspberries in a blender with 2 tablespoons water_ the granulated sugar_ lime zest and lime juice. Strain to remove the seeds. Top the cake with confectioners_ sugar_ the sauce and the remaining raspberries.','https://scontent-b.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-xap1/v/t1.0-9/s130x130/60910_450744008316781_1037819730_n.jpg?oh=d59c3d84b3da713b089f874bfd3670b5&oe=54ED2D89','https://www.facebook.com/365cps/photos/a.380809678643548.87582.378004348924081/450744008316781/?type=1&relevant_count=1','facebook.com','2012-12-12T07:07:47+0000',1355296067,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'378004348924081_450744018316780','https://www.facebook.com/378004348924081/posts/450744018316780','365 Cancer Prevention Society',423,'2014-10-29 05:01:35',1),('photo','post_page_378004348924081','Attitude is a little thing that makes a big difference','https://scontent-a.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-xap1/v/t1.0-9/s130x130/45160_450743558316826_922620776_n.jpg?oh=7699b38d36c83114459204913d34a43a&oe=54F0453B','https://www.facebook.com/365cps/photos/a.380809678643548.87582.378004348924081/450743558316826/?type=1&relevant_count=1','facebook.com','2012-12-12T07:05:24+0000',1355295924,3,3,0,0,0,0,0,3,'378004348924081_450743571650158','https://www.facebook.com/378004348924081/posts/450743571650158','365 Cancer Prevention Society',424,'2014-10-29 05:01:35',1),('photo','post_page_378004348924081','Life is a song - sing it.   Life is a game - play it.   Life is a challenge - meet it.   Life is a dream - realize it.   Life is a sacrifice - offer it.   Life is love - enjoy it.','https://fbcdn-sphotos-f-a.akamaihd.net/hphotos-ak-xpa1/v/t1.0-9/s130x130/155923_449895541734961_1113927713_n.jpg?oh=e8d17793da60249f1cf7c7b229230508&oe=54B7FC9A&__gda__=1425273880_cb9a21f512e6c70ed18df9f2cbd13997','https://www.facebook.com/365cps/photos/a.380809678643548.87582.378004348924081/449895541734961/?type=1&relevant_count=1','facebook.com','2012-12-10T10:16:11+0000',1355134571,7,7,0,0,0,0,0,7,'378004348924081_449895565068292','https://www.facebook.com/378004348924081/posts/449895565068292','365 Cancer Prevention Society',425,'2014-10-29 05:01:35',1),('status','post_page_378004348924081','We will be celebrating Christmas in advance today with our cancer patients and volunteers! WOOOHOOOO!! (:',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2012-12-08T02:50:18+0000',1354935018,3,3,0,0,0,0,0,3,'378004348924081_448936951830820','https://www.facebook.com/378004348924081/posts/448936951830820','365 Cancer Prevention Society',426,'2014-10-29 05:01:35',1),('photo','post_user_378004348924081',NULL,'https://fbcdn-sphotos-c-a.akamaihd.net/hphotos-ak-xap1/v/t1.0-9/s480x480/65163_176157182530818_893234645_n.jpg?oh=bb3e4a3f57f65760b309f84d30b0986e&oe=54AC3C52&__gda__=1421160458_e08261bfc2101994aa6a49efca7aa2d5','https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=176157182530818&set=o.378004348924081&type=1','facebook.com','2012-12-07T16:33:14+0000',1354897994,1,1,0,0,0,0,0,1,'378004348924081_176157182530818','https://www.facebook.com/378004348924081/posts/176157182530818','365 Cancer Prevention Society',427,'2014-10-29 05:01:35',1),('photo','post_page_378004348924081','365 Cancer Prevention Society added a new photo.','https://scontent-b.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-ash2/v/t1.0-9/s130x130/530466_448105538580628_1562208748_n.jpg?oh=e96758192ed7128f6203fd5e137457f7&oe=54EE33FD','https://www.facebook.com/365cps/photos/a.380809678643548.87582.378004348924081/448105538580628/?type=1&relevant_count=1','facebook.com','2012-12-06T02:54:47+0000',1354762487,5,5,0,0,0,0,0,5,'378004348924081_448105555247293','https://www.facebook.com/378004348924081/posts/448105555247293','365 Cancer Prevention Society',428,'2014-10-29 05:01:35',1),('photo','post_page_378004348924081','Peasant-Style Potato and Kale Soup!    SERVINGS  8  INGREDIENTS  6 ounces chorizo_ cut in half lengthwise and sliced  1 tablespoon olive oil  1 onion_ chopped  8 cups turkey or chicken stock  8 potatoes_ peeled and sliced  6 cloves garlic_ peeled_ root ends trimmed  1 bunch kale_ trimmed_ washed and thinly sliced  salt_ to taste  freshly ground black pepper_ to taste    PREPARATION  1. Heat a small skillet over medium heat. Add chorizo and cook_ stirring_ until browned_ about 5 minutes. Drain the chorizo on paper towels and set aside.    2. In a heavy stockpot_ heat oil over medium heat. Add onions and saute until softened_ 5 to 10 minutes. Add turkey or chicken stock_ potatoes and garlic and bring to a boil. Reduce heat to low and simmer_ uncovered_ until potatoes are tender_ 10 to 15 minutes.    3. With a slotted spoon_ transfer the potatoes and garlic to a bowl; lightly mash with a fork. Return to the soup and bring to a simmer. Stir in kale_ a handful at a time. Simmer for 5 minutes_ or until the kale is tender. Stir in the reserved chorizo and season with salt and pepper.    SERVING SUGGESTION  Enjoy with Whole Wheat Irish Soda Bread.    NUTRITION  (based on individual servings)  Calories: 251  Total Fat: 12 g  Cholesterol: 23 mg  Sodium: 382 mg  Carbohydrates: 27 g  Protein: 11 g        Read more: http://www.thedailygreen.com/healthy-eating/recipes/potato-kale-soup-recipe#ixzz2EEih7yfd','https://fbcdn-sphotos-a-a.akamaihd.net/hphotos-ak-xap1/v/t1.0-9/p130x130/12123_448104761914039_1446849423_n.jpg?oh=f8bbf6b4d4e47ade845d15db895ef6f3&oe=54BF359F&__gda__=1425201394_a813490264d1a85222562714d491a7dd','https://www.facebook.com/365cps/photos/a.380809678643548.87582.378004348924081/448104761914039/?type=1&relevant_count=1','facebook.com','2012-12-06T02:51:13+0000',1354762273,4,4,0,0,0,0,0,4,'378004348924081_448104778580704','https://www.facebook.com/378004348924081/posts/448104778580704','365 Cancer Prevention Society',429,'2014-10-29 05:01:35',1),('photo','post_page_378004348924081','Make something simple for your breakfast today! Banana and Almond Butter Toast    Resistant Starch: 5.6g    Ingredients: Almond butter_ rye bread_ banana     Calories: 280','https://fbcdn-sphotos-e-a.akamaihd.net/hphotos-ak-xaf1/v/t1.0-9/s130x130/399197_448103508580831_1639675547_n.jpg?oh=06eadbf949593862c3e312248f1fc106&oe=54B4C860&__gda__=1425569351_a620310db635c21c77960f67fd063298','https://www.facebook.com/365cps/photos/a.380809678643548.87582.378004348924081/448103508580831/?type=1&relevant_count=1','facebook.com','2012-12-06T02:46:00+0000',1354761960,7,7,0,0,0,0,0,7,'378004348924081_448103521914163','https://www.facebook.com/378004348924081/posts/448103521914163','365 Cancer Prevention Society',430,'2014-10-29 05:01:35',1),('photo','post_page