78004348924081/436769899714192/?type=1&relevant_count=1','facebook.com','2012-11-07T02:19:28+0000',1352254768,3,4,0,0,0,0,0,3,'378004348924081_436769913047524','https://www.facebook.com/378004348924081/posts/436769913047524','365 Cancer Prevention Society',510,'2014-10-29 05:01:35',1),('photo','post_page_378004348924081','365 Cancer Prevention Society added a new photo.','https://scontent-b.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-xpa1/v/t1.0-9/s130x130/59607_436071319784050_1552645414_n.jpg?oh=6aa9dbf65cb6a41a64d3067dbd65399a&oe=54F2722F','https://www.facebook.com/365cps/photos/a.380809678643548.87582.378004348924081/436071319784050/?type=1&relevant_count=1','facebook.com','2012-11-05T05:14:55+0000',1352092495,4,4,0,0,0,0,0,4,'378004348924081_436071329784049','https://www.facebook.com/378004348924081/posts/436071329784049','365 Cancer Prevention Society',511,'2014-10-29 05:01:35',1),('photo','post_page_378004348924081','Cucumber Salad With Coriander       Ingredients (Serves 2)  Sea salt  2 cucumbers  2 tablespoon white wine vinegar  pinch of ground paprika  pinch of cane sugar  1 carrot  1 tablespoon olive oil  Pinch of curry powder  10 coriander seeds  1 garlic clove    How To Prepare Cucumber Salad With Coriander:  Measure a teaspoons of sea salt into a bowl.  Peel the cucumber and slice thinly_ then cut into strips.  Combine well and leave to stand for 10 minutes.  Squeeze out_ and pour away the liquid.  Add the vinegar_ ground paprika and cane sugar.  Wash the carrot_ peel_ and grate thinly onto the cucumber.  Add the olive oil _ curry powder_  and  coriander seeds.  Peel the garlic_ chop finely_ and add to the rest of the ingredients.  Combine well and season with a little salt.','https://fbcdn-sphotos-h-a.akamaihd.net/hphotos-ak-ash2/v/t1.0-9/s130x130/521617_436070579784124_1329337919_n.jpg?oh=c0a99aa905b94076fe49af0a90ecd6c7&oe=54F8AE6F&__gda__=1421198837_e84d9d87c6c0ddd96508ed12106fc1bf','https://www.facebook.com/365cps/photos/a.380809678643548.87582.378004348924081/436070579784124/?type=1&relevant_count=1','facebook.com','2012-11-05T05:11:02+0000',1352092262,1,2,0,0,0,0,0,1,'378004348924081_436070616450787','https://www.facebook.com/378004348924081/posts/436070616450787','365 Cancer Prevention Society',512,'2014-10-29 05:01:35',1),('photo','post_page_378004348924081','Exercise Lowers Breast Cancer Risk    One hour of walking at a 2 to 3 mph pace lowers your risk a little. Three to five hours weekly of brisk walking gives you the most protection from breast cancer. You could vary that by switching activities -- try jogging_ hiking_ swimming_ cycling_ or other activities that get you moving.','https://scontent-b.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-frc3/v/t1.0-9/s130x130/533584_436068216451027_1401409514_n.jpg?oh=8618553d6879fdcb677acfd50d34f406&oe=54C16F8A','https://www.facebook.com/365cps/photos/a.380809678643548.87582.378004348924081/436068216451027/?type=1&relevant_count=1','facebook.com','2012-11-05T04:58:53+0000',1352091533,1,1,0,0,0,0,0,1,'378004348924081_436068226451026','https://www.facebook.com/378004348924081/posts/436068226451026','365 Cancer Prevention Society',513,'2014-10-29 05:01:35',1),('photo','post_page_378004348924081','Express Your Emotions Appropriately    Traditional Chinese Medicine (TCM) has always recognized that emotional factors play an important role in health and illness and notes seven emotions that particularly affect the body: joy_ anger_ sadness_ grief_ pensiveness_ fear and fright. These emotions are not by themselves thought to be pathological and all constitute emotional aspects of healthy people. However_ if any of these emotions are excessive over a long period of time or arises suddenly with great force_ it can generate imbalances and illness.    If holding in emotions or expressing them in inappropriate ways can lead to health imbalances which may lead to illness_ endeavoring to express our positive and negative emotions in appropriate ways can be as preventive as exercising or eating a balanced diet. In our society_ this takes awareness and careful choices of words as the expression of _negative_ emotions such as anger or sadness is often discouraged socially. Nonetheless_ it is important to be in touch with our feelings and to express them in an authentic way.','https://scontent-b.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-xfa1/v/t1.0-9/p130x130/31029_435207459870436_476395127_n.jpg?oh=0cadac75db8d43c90e419988f775e3f6&oe=54B4B679','https://www.facebook.com/365cps/photos/a.380809678643548.87582.378004348924081/435207459870436/?type=1&relevant_count=1','facebook.com','2012-11-03T04:32:12+0000',1351917132,3,3,0,0,0,0,0,3,'378004348924081_435207479870434','https://www.facebook.com/378004348924081/posts/435207479870434','365 Cancer Prevention Society',514,'2014-10-29 05:01:35',1),('photo','post_page_378004348924081','Always believe something good is about to happen. Think positive! Have a great weekend everyone! (:','https://scontent-b.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-xfa1/v/t1.0-9/s130x130/550171_435204766537372_1747809047_n.jpg?oh=0c8598498b5a1979c5d5e213d4daf64d&oe=54C0025E','https://www.facebook.com/365cps/photos/a.380809678643548.87582.378004348924081/435204766537372/?type=1&relevant_count=1','facebook.com','2012-11-03T04:17:38+0000',1351916258,2,2,0,0,0,0,0,2,'378004348924081_435204776537371','https://www.facebook.com/378004348924081/posts/435204776537371','365 Cancer Prevention Society',515,'2014-10-29 05:01:35',1),('status','post_page_378004348924081','Although making healthy selections at the grocery store and at mealtime can_t guarantee cancer prevention_ it may help reduce your risk (: Take plenty of fruits and veggies!',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2012-11-03T04:06:23+0000',1351915583,3,3,0,0,0,0,0,3,'378004348924081_435202143204301','https://www.facebook.com/378004348924081/posts/435202143204301','365 Cancer Prevention Society',516,'2014-10-29 05:01:35',1),('status','post_page_378004348924081','Concerned about cancer prevention? Take charge by making small changes in your daily life_ from eating a healthy diet