ixture. Let stand for 5 to 10 minutes.  Add eggs_ vanilla_ sweetener_ and oil. Mix well.  Add dry ingredients and mix well.  Heat a skillet or griddle to medium heat.  Pour 1/4 cup of batter onto heated skillet for each pancake and spread out the batter a little (so itâ€™s even and flat).  Let cook until bubbles form on the top.  Flip* and cook the other side until golden brown.    *Only flip once. These pancakes stay very moist inside.','https://fbcdn-sphotos-c-a.akamaihd.net/hphotos-ak-xaf1/v/t1.0-9/s130x130/425812_428010417256807_1123299273_n.jpg?oh=785b8798ca853c664192817b31548096&oe=54AAE452&__gda__=1424931701_4dda3d2f4b9a6fd715cfe3cfc67f94b7','https://www.facebook.com/365cps/photos/a.380809678643548.87582.378004348924081/428010417256807/?type=1&relevant_count=1','facebook.com','2012-10-18T03:43:51+0000',1350531831,5,5,6,6,0,0,5,16,'378004348924081_428010430590139','https://www.facebook.com/378004348924081/posts/428010430590139','365 Cancer Prevention Society',565,'2014-10-29 05:01:35',1),('status','post_page_378004348924081','Cancer victims who don_t accept their fate_ who don_t learn to live with it_ will only destroy what little time they have left.',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2012-10-18T03:31:01+0000',1350531061,1,1,0,0,0,0,0,1,'378004348924081_428007393923776','https://www.facebook.com/378004348924081/posts/428007393923776','365 Cancer Prevention Society',566,'2014-10-29 05:01:35',1),('status','post_page_378004348924081','If you would like to make monthly donation to us_ pm me for the application form for INTERBANK GIRO.',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2012-10-18T03:23:33+0000',1350530613,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'378004348924081_428004923924023','https://www.facebook.com/378004348924081/posts/428004923924023','365 Cancer Prevention Society',567,'2014-10-29 05:01:35',1),('photo','post_page_378004348924081','Carrots are rich in Vitamin A! Carrot is one of the best cancer fighting foods. The vegetable reduces the cancer cells affecting the mouth_ throat_ stomach_ intestine_ bladder_ prostate_