 and 17 grahams of protein. The recipe is great for those on a soft food diet. Patients on fiber-restricted diets should count the dry milk in this recipe as 1/4 cup of their daily milk allowance. Those on low lactose diets should use 1 tbsp. of soy formula in place of the dry milk and water.   Read more: Recipes for Cancer Patients & Families | eHow.com http://www.ehow.com/way_5390933_recipes-cancer-patients-families.html#ixzz28lDJxwAj','https://fbexternal-a.akamaihd.net/safe_image.php?d=AQDHGwlQj0xXWD3g&w=158&h=158&url=http%3A%2F%2Fv5-static.ehowcdn.com%2Fmedia%2Fvendor%2Ffacebook%2Fog-images%2Ffb_logo.jpg','http://www.ehow.com/way_5390933_recipes-cancer-patients-families.html#ixzz28lDJxwAj','ehow.com','2012-10-09T01:21:17+0000',1349745677,2,2,0,0,0,0,0,2,'378004348924081_147831505363163','https://www.facebook.com/378004348924081/posts/147831505363163','365 Cancer Prevention Society',585,'2014-10-29 05:01:35',1),('status','post_page_378004348924081','Foods high in bad fats_ sugar and chemicals are directly linked to many negative emotions_ whereas whole_ natural foods rich in nutrients - foods such as fruits_ vegetables_ grains and legumes - contribute to greater energy and positive emotions.',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2012-10-08T09:25:03+0000',1349688303,7,7,0,0,0,0,0,7,'378004348924081_424149080976274','https://www.facebook.com/378004348924081/posts/424149080976274','365 Cancer Prevention Society',586,'2014-10-29 05:01:35',1),('video','post_page_378004348924081','The belly rules the mind! Start eating fresh fruits now and cut down on red meat!','https://fbexternal-a.akamaihd.net/safe_image.php?d=AQDr0iOcKHk3fAj2&w=130&h=130&url=http%3A%2F%2Fi2.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FiZf5YJJf8ds%2Fmqdefault.jpg','http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iZf5YJJf8ds','youtube.com','2012-10-08T09:22:55+0000',1349688175,4,4,0,0,0,0,0,4,'378004348924081_364364356981182','https://www.facebook.com/378004348924081/posts/364364356981182','365 Cancer Prevention Society',587,'2014-10-29 05:01:35',1),('status','post