 at least 69 can cause cancer.    Credits:National Cancer Institute','https://scontent-b.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-xfa1/v/t1.0-9/s130x130/1000885_533904080000773_325868552_n.jpg?oh=e273f0cff6125c3bfb1166e433f1f610&oe=54AAB955','https://www.facebook.com/365cps/photos/a.380809678643548.87582.378004348924081/533904080000773/?type=1&relevant_count=1','facebook.com','2013-06-13T07:09:51+0000',1371107391,1,1,0,0,0,0,0,1,'378004348924081_533904086667439','https://www.facebook.com/378004348924081/posts/533904086667439','365 Cancer Prevention Society',672,'2014-10-29 05:02:21',1),('photo','post_page_378004348924081','Prevent Colorectal Cancer with FISHES!!!    A new study_ published in the American Journal of Clinical Nutrition_ surveyed the eating habits of more than 5_300 people who also came in for a colonoscopy. The women who ate the most fish (three times a week) were 33 percent less likely to have polyps_ growths of tissue that accumulate in the colon and are considered to be precursors to cancer.     Researchers believe that the anti-inflammatory properties of the omega-3s found in fish are responsible for preventing these polyps from forming in the first place. Interestingly_ this same link was not found in men. Researchers speculate that men could be less sensitive to omega-3s and would need to eat greater quantities to reap the same benefits as women.    Other health tips on omega-3s:   - Omega-3s_ also found in walnuts_ leafy greens_ and flax seeds  - It is also proven to improve heart health_ boost mood_ and alleviate dry skin.    Extract from prevention.com','https://fbcdn-sphotos-e-a.akamaihd.net/hphotos-ak-frc3/v/t1.0-9/s130x130/1013011_533862390004942_607170286_n.jpg?oh=3a33daebb73ecfef9dcb79f87ac2ba7b&oe=54EC0E88&__gda__=1425311715_f4fec5bf27c344befd0b98fd78095ab3','https://www.facebook.com/365cps/photos/a.380809678643548.87582.378004348924081/533862390004942/?type=1&relevant_count=1','facebook.com','2013-06-13T05:04:19+0000',1371099859,1,1,0,0,0,0,0,1,'378004348924081_533862400004941','https://www.facebook.com/378004348924081/posts/533862400004941','365 Cancer Prevention Society',673,'2014-10-29 05:02:21',1),('photo','post_page_378004348924081','Make a Blackberry-Banana Smoothie!     Food tips: Blackberries are rich in disease-fighting antioxidants.     What ingredients do you need?   2 cupsfrozen blackberries   1 small banana_ sliced   1/2 cuplight coconut milk   1/2 cupplain low-fat yogurt   2 tablespoonslemon juice   1 tablespoonhoney   1 teaspoongrated lemon zest     Preparation (10mins)   Process blackberries_ banana_ coconut milk_ yogurt_ lemon juice_ honey_ and lemon zest in a blender until smooth. Divide the mixture evenly into 2 chilled glasses_ and you ready to drink!     -An extract from health.com','https://scontent-a.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-xaf1/v/t1.0-9/p130x130/1005114_533044266753421_267957994_n.jpg?oh=b8d1af1269d2ca4f1b889d258994c38b&oe=54C26EAF','https://www.facebook.com/365cps/photos/a.380809678643548.87582.378004348924081/533044266753421/?type=1&relevant_count=1','facebook.com','2013-06-11T06:21:02+0000',1370931662,6,6,0,0,0,0,0,6,'378004348924081_533044273420087','https://www.facebook.com/378004348924081/posts/533044273420087','365 Cancer Prevention Society',674,'2014-10-29 05:02:21',1),('photo','post_page_378004348924081','WHAT ARE THE 6 CANCER FIGHTNG SUPER FOOD?    6. Black Beans    Black Bean has an impressive array of antioxidant and anti-inflammatory phytonutrients. Numerous studies have connected black bean intake with reduced risk of certain cancers_ especially colon cancer. Chronic excessive oxidative stress and chronic excessive inflammatory are both risk factors for the development of many cancer types. By increasing the body_s supply of antioxidant and anti-inflammatory nutrients_ black beans may be able to help lower cancer risk.     Helps fight: breast and colon cancers     -Extract from Health.com and Whfoods.com','https://scontent-b.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-xfa1/v/t1.0-9/s130x130/1001830_532651346792713_1628479207_n.jpg?oh=29790ea5df2b5f7775f978b9e910cdc0&oe=54AAFC25','https://www.facebook.com/365cps/photos/a.380809678643548.87582.378004348924081/532651346792713/?type=1&relevant_count=1','facebook.com','2013-06-10T07:01:38+0000',1370847698,4,4,0,0,0,1,0,5,'378004348924081_532651353459379','https://www.facebook.com/378004348924081/posts/532651353459379','365 Cancer Prevention Society',675,'2014-10-29 05:02:21',1),('link','post_page_378004348924081','Chemotherapy may causes side effects that affect your appetite_taste and digestive system. Click to read up on this _15 Nutrition Tips_ for those who are coping chemotherapy.  Fight on fighters!',NULL,'http://www.webmd.com/ovarian-cancer/features/15-nutrition-tips-chemo','webmd.com','2013-06-07T09:46:26+0000',1370598386,2,2,0,0,0,1,0,3,'378004348924081_531441673580347','https://www.facebook.com/378004348924081/posts/531441673580347','365 Cancer Prevention Society',676,'2014-10-29 05:02:21',1),('photo','post_page_378004348924081','WHAT ARE THE 6 CANCER FIGHTNG SUPER FOOD?     5. Broccoli     All cruciferous veggies (think cauliflower_ cabbage_ kale) contain cancer-fighting properties_ but broccoli is the only one with a sizable amount of sulforaphane_ a particularly potent compound that boosts the body_s protective enzymes and flushes out cancer-causing chemicals_ says Jed Fahey_ ScD. A recent University of Michigan study on mice found that sulforaphane also targets cancer stem cellsâ€”those that aid in tumor growth.     Helps fight: breast_ liver_ lung_ prostate_ skin_ stomach_ and bladder cancers     -Extract from health.com','https://scontent-a.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-ash2/v/t1.0-9/s130x130/945516_530907730300408_1020812155_n.jpg?oh=19b970dbed766022420b959e983cca87&oe=54BB6B3C','https://www.facebook.com/365cps/photos/a.380809678643548.87582.378004348924081/530907730300408/?type=1&relevant_count=1','facebook.com','2013-06-06T05:40:28+0000',1370497228,2,2,0,0,0,2,0,4,'378004348924081_530907736967074','https://www.facebook.com/378004348924081/posts/530907736967074','365 Cancer Prevention Society',677,'2014-10-29 05:02:21',1),('photo','post_page_378004348924081','Want to find out more about ovarian cancer? check this out!','https://scontent-a.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-xaf1/v/t1.0-9/s130x130/944305_588037671226694_1219787713_n.jpg?oh=432e72c673787957148161634fa724ac&oe=54ECDDCC','https://www.facebook.com/sgcancersociety/photos/a.594842270546234.1073741833.238763499487448/588037671226694/?type=1','facebook.com','2013-06-01T03:59:06+0000',1370059146,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'378004348924081_528585750532606','https://www.facebook.com/378004348924081/posts/528585750532606','365 Cancer Prevention Society',678,'2014-10-29 05:02:21',1),('photo','post_page_378004348924081','WHAT ARE THE 6 CANCER-FIGHTING SUPER FOOD?    4. Berries    All berries are packed with cancer-fighting phytonutrients. But black raspberries_ in particular_ contain very high concentrations of phytochemicals called anthocyanins_ which slow down the growth of premalignant cells and keep new blood vessels from forming (and potentially feeding a cancerous tumor)_ according to Gary D. Stoner_ PhD_ a professor of internal medicine at The Ohio State University College of Medicine.     Helps fight: colon_ esophageal_ oral_ and skin cancers     -Extract from health.com','https://fbcdn-sphotos-c-a.akamaihd.net/hphotos-ak-prn2/v/t1.0-9/s130x130/954797_528584547199393_271331255_n.jpg?oh=7bda0688661febadea1c92ccf39adff3&oe=54C089BD&__gda__=1425389772_71677056e0c38f3ac353ef8aaeb927a9','https://www.facebook.com/365cps/photos/a.380809678643548.87582.378004348924081/528584547199393/?type=1&relevant_count=1','facebook.com','2013-06-01T03:54:28+0000',1370058868,4,4,0,0,0,1,0,5,'378004348924081_528584557199392','https://www.facebook.com/378004348924081/posts/528584557199392','365 Cancer Prevention Society',679,'2014-10-29 05:02:21',1),('photo','post_page_378004348924081','365 Cancer Prevention Society shared a photo.','https://scontent-b.xx.fbcdn