wth in a study in Nutrition and Cancer. Endometrial cancer causes nearly 8_000 deaths a year.     Helps fight: endometrial_ lung_ prostate_ and stomach cancers     -extract from health.com','https://fbcdn-sphotos-c-a.akamaihd.net/hphotos-ak-xap1/v/t1.0-9/s130x130/960045_522321784492336_279351514_n.jpg?oh=b554c47c3aa1458fe61d1dba21ed0452&oe=54F3957E&__gda__=1421012499_4b7513f7ac9ce2bcdd1033448abb6eef','https://www.facebook.com/365cps/photos/a.380809678643548.87582.378004348924081/522321784492336/?type=1&relevant_count=1','facebook.com','2013-05-17T09:59:40+0000',1368784780,1,1,0,0,0,0,0,1,'378004348924081_522321794492335','https://www.facebook.com/378004348924081/posts/522321794492335','365 Cancer Prevention Society',686,'2014-10-29 05:02:21',1),('photo','post_page_378004348924081','WHAT ARE THE 6 CANCER FIGHTING SUPER FOOD?    1.Garlic    Phytochemicals in garlic have been found to halt the formation of nitrosamines_ carcinogens formed in the stomach (and in the intestines_ in certain conditions) when you consume nitrates_ a common food preservative_ BÃ©liveau says. In fact_ the Iowa Women_s Health Study found that women with the highest amounts of garlic in their diets had a 50 percent lower risk of certain colon cancers than women who ate the least.    Helps fight: breast_ colon_ esophageal_ and stomach cancers    Do add some garlic to your meals today! :)    -extract from health.com','https://fbcdn-sphotos-d-a.akamaihd.net/hphotos-ak-ash2/v/t1.0-9/s130x130/486715_521876044536910_2012126684_n.jpg?oh=5d852e85b49131780eb0c5298967037f&oe=54BA7B68&__gda__=1425262322_af1133c3e67b5bfecf15d161c8933c4b','https://www.facebook.com/365cps/photos/a.380809678643548.87582.378004348924081/521876044536910/?type=1&relevant_count=1','facebook.com','2013-05-16T03:46:53+0000',1368676013,1,1,0,0,0,1,0,2,'378004348924081_521876051203576','https://www.facebook.com/378004348924081/posts/521876051203576','365 Cancer Prevention Society',687,'2014-10-29 05:02:21',1),('photo','post_page_37