nd lemon zest to a boil in a saucepan over medium-high heat. Reduce heat to medium-low_ and simmer until slightly thickened_ about 5 minutes. Remove from heat_ and stir in vanilla extract. Set aside to cool.  Layer the fruit in a large_ clear glass bowl in this order: pineapple_ strawberries_ kiwi fruit_ bananas_ oranges_ grapes_ and blueberries. Pour the cooled sauce over the fruit. Cover and refrigerate for 3 to 4 hours before serving.','https://scontent-b.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-xpa1/v/t1.0-9/s130x130/61709_479318628792652_1941260850_n.jpg?oh=5817424b59db63db2b5334231757f87c&oe=54BAE444','https://www.facebook.com/365cps/photos/a.380809678643548.87582.378004348924081/479318628792652/?type=1&relevant_count=1','facebook.com','2013-02-06T09:18:33+0000',1360142313,5,5,0,0,0,0,0,5,'378004348924081_479318675459314','https://www.facebook.com/378004348924081/posts/479318675459314','365 Cancer Prevention Society',752,'2014-10-29 05:02:21',1),('status','post_page_378004348924081','å½“æˆ‘ä»¬çš„å®¶äººè¿˜åœ¨çš„æ—¶å€™ï¼Œæˆ‘ä»¬è¦çˆ±ä»–ä»¬ï¼Œçæƒœç€å®Œç¾Žçš„å®¶åº­ï¼Œçæƒœæ¯ä¸€ä¸ªçè´µçš„æ—¶åˆ» ã€‚æ¯å¤©æ´»å¾—å¿«å¿«ä¹ä¹ã€‚',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2013-01-29T07:32:20+0000',1359444740,4,4,0,0,0,0,0,4,'378004348924081_472580822799766','https://www.facebook.com/378004348924081/posts/472580822799766','365 Cancer Prevention Society',753,'2014-10-29 05:02:21',1),('photo','post_page_378004348924081','Peach Pear Apple Juice Fruit juice Recipe. Very simple and easy to make.    All you need is....  1 apple_ cored and sliced  2 peaches_ remove seed  1 pear_ sliced      Process through a juicer and serve.','https://fbcdn-sphotos-h-a.akamaihd.net/hphotos-ak-ash2/v/t1.0-9/s130x130/537299_472577589466756_788418933_n.jpg?oh=821e89006d2954517846a9ff215110ba&oe=54AA0747&__gda__=1421523989_d48eb2469a5dd4d9798ce809a97ec7c3','https://www.facebook.com/365cps/photos/a.380809678643548.87582.378004348924081/472577589466756/?type=1&relevant_count=1','facebook.com','2013-01-29T07:20:01+0000',1359444001,3,4,0,0