upon me because I_m a girl. Pink was silly; sissy. Blue was strong; secure.  ...  Now that I_m on the other side_ I kind of like pink. I know that may be a surprise. Now I get it. That pink ribbon is a badge of courage_ symbolizing a battle hard fought. I guess you can say I_ve embraced the pink. I now wear the color with honor and proudly proclaim _I_m a survivor._ I_m not a victim.','https://scontent-b.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-xpf1/v/t1.0-9/s130x130/311933_10150955934980462_1571002249_n.jpg?oh=7962b9c023ea91ac123796d70495e87a&oe=54C1F3F0','https://www.facebook.com/dartmouthcancer/photos/a.10150955830605462.763729.10150117443575462/10150955934980462/?type=1&relevant_count=1','facebook.com','2011-11-23T15:54:33+0000',1322063673,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'10150117443575462_10150955960065462','https://www.facebook.com/10150117443575462/posts/10150955960065462','Norris Cotton Cancer Center',24077,'2014-10-29 12:06:03',1),('photo','post_page_10150117443575462','2011 Dartmouth Hitchcock','https://fbcdn-sphotos-f-a.akamaihd.net/hphotos-ak-xfa1/v/t1.0-9/s130x130/318598_10150955953570462_397222207_n.jpg?oh=2858972ebe10879bb3b91c77cb528f29&oe=54CAA609&__gda__=1420846169_c09e3d60da0d895b35f38ce532038620','https://www.facebook.com/dartmouthcancer/photos/a.10150955830605462.763729.10150117443575462/10150955953570462/?type=1&relevant_count=1','facebook.com','2011-11-23T15:54:33+0000',1322063673,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'10150117443575462_10150955960070462','https://www.facebook.com/10150117443575462/posts/10150955960070462','Norris Cotton Cancer Center',24078,'2014-10-29 12:06:03',1),('photo','post_page_10150117443575462','Victoria McCandless and Parker Towle_ MD_ listen to Sheila Drury read her poetry.','https://scontent-b.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-xpf1/v/t1.0-9/s130x130/304064_10150955930895462_969156752_n.jpg?oh=1c6fa6ee031ff31caf915d19eab3ff40&oe=54BFEFEA','https://www.facebook.com/dartmouthcancer/photos/a.10150955830605462.763729.10150117443575462/10150955930895462/?type=1&relevant_count=1','facebook.