e of things. For example_ youâ€™re thankful that they found a treatment for you_ but youâ€™re grieving the loss of your hair. Donâ€™t feel bad for your grief. It doesnâ€™t mean youâ€™re ungrateful. Take one day at a time. You cry one day_ feel bad; the next day you have to get up and smile and believe that life goes on. Donâ€™t dwell on optimism or pessimism. Realistically embrace what you are going through. Believe_ believe_ believe. Just believe.  â€”Anonymous','https://scontent-a.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-xap1/v/t1.0-9/s130x130/1235302_10153165297150462_764613779_n.jpg?oh=ba33a0541dcb4fcea97b93817fef983e&oe=54CE1AB2','https://www.facebook.com/dartmouthcancer/photos/a.10150269922540462.502490.10150117443575462/10153165297150462/?type=1&relevant_count=1','facebook.com','2013-09-04T15:30:53+0000',1378308653,8,8,0,0,0,0,0,8,'10150117443575462_10153165297265462','https://www.facebook.com/10150117443575462/posts/10153165297265462','Norris Cotton Cancer Center',24663,'2014-10-29 12:07:16',1),('photo','post_page_10150117443575462','_It was like walking onto a spaceship._      See a video about our newest linear accelerator and hear from patients and staff.     http://cancer.dartmouth.edu/focus/linear_accelerator_Varian_Truebeam_radiation_therapists.html','https://fbcdn-sphotos-c-a.akamaihd.net/hphotos-ak-xap1/v/t1.0-9/s130x130/1234785_10153148980100462_1035693210_n.jpg?oh=89c6e76e19d96b20072111eb1a83bf0e&oe=54BAE96E&__gda__=1420645719_d743b31f191674121aeb12b9d89f5c6d','https://www.facebook.com/dartmouthcancer/photos/a.10150269922540462.502490.10150117443575462/10153148980100462/?type=1&relevant_count=1','facebook.com','2013-09-01T23:00:02+0000',1378076402,19,19,4,4,0,0,3,26,'10150117443575462_10153156338980462','https://www.facebook.com/10150117443575462/posts/10153156338980462','Norris Cotton Cancer Center',24664,'2014-10-29 12:07:16',1),('video','post_page_10150117443575462','What_s all the fuss about? Judge for yourself. Are these fast food ads aimed at kids about the food