 at greater risk for frostbite if they have treatment side effects_ such as peripheral neuropathy (a nerve disorder)_ that cause them to be less sensitive to temperature extremes.   Learn what precautions you can take.....',NULL,'http://www.cancer.net/all-about-cancer/cancernet-feature-articles/side-effects/cancer-and-winter-months','cancer.net','2013-02-09T13:00:01+0000',1360414801,2,2,0,0,0,0,0,2,'10150117443575462_345432578904576','https://www.facebook.com/10150117443575462/posts/345432578904576','Norris Cotton Cancer Center',24824,'2014-10-29 12:07:16',1),('link','post_page_10150117443575462','On this silent snowy day_ I took the time to read this article and watch the 60-Minutes video featuring Dr. Ira Byock.   I wish my father had gone to hospice sooner when he was dying of colon cancer in 2009. Hospice was a much better place for our family to support his passing. What do you think it means to die well?  -dd','https://fbexternal-a.akamaihd.net/safe_image.php?d=AQBFcvoq-752DHSY&w=158&h=158&url=http%3A%2F%2Fi.i.com.com%2Fcnwk.1d%2Fi%2Ftim%2F2013%2F02%2F05%2FCrimesider_0205_JailFlipBird_300x225.jpg','http://www.cbsnews.com/8301-204_162-57567998/end-of-life-care-for-elderly-often-too-aggressive-study-says/','cbsnews.com','2013-02-08T15:05:18+0000',1360335918,1,1,0,0,0,0,0,1,'10150117443575462_153139391508529','https://www.facebook.com/10150117443575462/posts/153139391508529','Norris Cotton Cancer Center',24825,'2014-10-29 12:07:16',1),('photo','post_page_10150117443575462','It_s supposed to snow tomorrow. So if you want to hit the slopes... check out this great deal for Moms that benefits the Southwestern Regional Cancer Center in Bennington. ','https://scontent-b.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-xfa1/v/t1.0-9/s130x130/544465_10151284205040687_595354137_n.jpg?oh=20ecba5c205bb7aa082617f30ff1c996&oe=54B03348','https://www.facebook.com/svmedicalcenter/photos/a.10150885713395687.412458.34778190686/10151284205040687/?type=1','facebook.com','2013-02-07T18:29:24+0000',1360261764,3,3,0,0,0,0,0,3,'10150117443575462_460001427388181','https://www.facebook.com/10150117443575462/posts/460001427388181','Norris Cotton Cancer Center',24826,'2014-10-29 12:07:16',1),('photo','post_page_10150117443575462','For 26 years_ David_s House has been a haven for more than 12_000 families whose children received medical treatment at CHaD. But so many people need its services that in the last five years_ they_ve had to turn away more than 921 families.   They_re raising money to expand their services_ including the construction of a four-bedroom addition that will allow David_s House to serve 90 percent of those they had to turn away. It will include a first-floor room with handicapped access; a separate area for breastfeeding mothers; and a renovated kitchen_ complete with breakfast nook.   The renovation should be finished by midsummer. It will add a total of 3_615 square feet_ with 2-1/2 baths_ storage space_ and an office_ sitting area and conference room.   As one past resident said: _The hospital is there to heal patients; David_s House is there to heal families._   Founded in honor of David Cyr_ who died in 1984 at age five_ David_s House is available to anyone who has a child receiving medical care at CHaD. They welcome families to stay as long as their child is in treatment. A voluntary donation of $20 a night is suggested_ but only 40 percent of families can afford to pay_ and no one will be turned away due to lack of funds.','https://scontent-a.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-frc3/v/t1.0-9/s130x130/598815_10151360356259484_897896887_n.jpg?oh=9542c3297bbaf259905785fe42663d0c&oe=54AF071E','https://www.facebook.com/davidshouseinc/photos/a.10151169657144484.465398.128863519483/10151360356259484/?type=1','facebook.com','2013-02-07T01:02:42+0000',1360198962,7,7,0,0,0,0,0,7,'10150117443575462_508317949207248','https://www.facebook.com/10150117443575462/posts/508317949207248','Norris Cotton Cancer Center',24827,'2014-10-29 12:07:16',1),('photo','post_page_1015011744357546