 and Mae. Since that day_ we have taken 15 trips and traveled nearly 25_000 miles. We will never be able to repay our debt to Sam_s supporters. There have been many moments over the past year when the excitement of our trips has given way to worries; it is easy in those moments to mourn what weâve lost. But_ as we sit here today_ with two healthy twin girls and Sam doing better than ever_ it is also easy to celebrate what weâve gained: a giving_ loving community organized around our little boy.   This year_ we want to spend more time giving back and ensuring that families like ours are given more options than we were. We are starting a non-profit organization called With Purpose_ and we intend to raise money for childhood cancer research. We hope to carry over this communal momentum around Sam to the thousands of other kids with cancer. We hope you share With Purpose with your networks! https://www.facebook.com/withpurposegiving?ref=hl_','https://fbcdn-profile-a.akamaihd.net/hprofile-ak-xfp1/v/t1.0-1/10678482_1471453426463396_7516239794190142111_n.png?oh=7e43f701b6a8f2b7a5af33c52dd29cd0&oe=54BC5ED4&__gda__=1421333548_b4c47025c91fc5f3e6ebf1a7ea297156','https://www.facebook.com/withpurposegiving','facebook.com','2014-07-27T17:12:49+0000',1406481169,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,0,'139407847155_931030526921684','https://www.facebook.com/139407847155/posts/931030526921684','Prevent Cancer Foundation',26510,'2014-10-29 13:13:49',1),('photo','post_page_139407847155','Are you a Nats fan with a bit of a competitive streak? We have just the contest for you!  Support Prevent Cancer and win two tickets to the Washington Nationals vs. New York Mets game on August 6th at 7:05pm. The Prevent Cancer 5k Walk/Run registered participant who raises the most amount of money from Friday_ July 25th to Friday_ August 1st at 5pm EST will take home the tickets and enjoy a night out at Nationals Park.  Start now! Register: https://www.preventcancer5k.org/Account/Register','https://fbcdn-sphotos-h-a.akam