 she can live with_ whom to believe_ what and how much to read. Unhappily_ there are no easy answers and no consensus about what or who is correct. Eleven years later we are still asking the same questions. It was long believed that cancers caught â€œearlyâ€ by mammography were less likely to be fatal. It is now known that some cancers are more aggressive than others_ and that the time of diagnosis or the size of the tumour may have little to do with long-term prospects. Please join us on May 15 to discuss the pertinent issues that surround mammography and make sense of the confusing messages about this loaded subject. When 7:00 pm. Where: 24 Mont-Royal West (Suite 603) Montreal_ QuÃ©bec.','https://scontent-b.xx.fbcdn.net/hphotos-xpa1/v/t1.0-9/p130x130/941909_558811357503875_499743926_n.jpg?oh=eaa6747734429c2231b5b2a15a504629&oe=54F6350B','https://www.facebook.com/PreventCancerNow/photos/a.210347069016974.70438.198826403502374/558811357503875/?type=1&relevant_count=1','facebook.com','2013-05-08T01:15:12+0000',1367975712,5,5,2,2,0,0,2,9,'198826403502374_558811364170541','https://www.facebook.com/198826403502374/posts/558811364170541','Prevent Cancer Now',26990,'2014-10-29 13:28:13',1),('link','post_page_198826403502374','Johnson & Johnson_s cosmetics licence pulled at Mumbai plant after carcinogenic substance discovered in talcum powder http://tinyurl.com/ToxicTalcum','https://fbexternal-a.akamaihd.net/safe_image.php?d=AQB6zfdI-rFdDRzW&w=158&h=158&url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cosmeticsdesign-asia.com%2Fvar%2Fplain_site%2Fstorage%2Fimages%2Fpublications%2Fcosmetics%2Fcosmeticsdesign-asia.com%2Fbusiness-financial%2Ffda-cancels-j-j-s-cosmetics-licence-at-mumbai-plant%2F8092494-1-eng-GB%2FFDA-cancels-J-J-s-cosmetics-licence-at-Mumbai-plant_medium_vga.jpg','http://www.cosmeticsdesign-asia.com/Business-Financial/FDA-cancels-J-J-s-cosmetics-licence-at-Mumbai-plant/?c=IIf0ZMUaLnwJGOYtAgIxUg%253D%253D&utm_source=newsletter_daily&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=GIN_CDd','cosmeticsdesig